data.description: Feast your eyes on this beautifully renovated raised ranch. This bright and inviting 5 bed 2 full bath home features tons of updates. You won't miss a beat as the living room, kitchen, diningroom flow from one space to the next. You'll notice all the new custom trim work and detials throughout. Restored HW flooring the flows through the 2nd floor. The upper level features 3 good sized bedrooms and a full bath. Head into the lower level where you have a, full bath, 2 extra bedroom, a great size laundry room additional hang our space perfect for movie nights or play room for the kids. Lovely backyard with a huge double teir deck, perfect for entertaining, play with the kids, host events; you can do it all. This property is completely move in ready and waiting for you to make it HOME!
